* {{rhymes|eɪʃən}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The feeling of extreme [[disgust]] and hatred; [[abhorrence]]; [[detestation]]; [[loathing]].
# That which is [[abominable]], [[shameful]]ly vile; an object or state that excites disgust and hatred; very often with religious undertones.
#* Antony, most large in his '''abominations'''. Shakespeare, ''Antony and Cleopatra, III-vi''

